                <author refid="100626755" vocab="viaf">unknown French</author>
                <position>silver mount</position>
                <text type="mark">Each silver mount bears a dove (the Paris discharge mark for small silver works used between May 6, 1722, and September 2, 1727, under the fermier Charles Cordier).</text>
